{"tid":15212,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"成功戒煙揮手區","createTime":"2016-12-01T01:27:27.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-06T09:19:02.000Z","uid":40194,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7d5589e007c30bb314f118756d40c9e1193a7466","tid":15212,"uid":40194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T01:27:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5989325134bdab661bc66a1932dafb94aa5f7583","tid":15212,"uid":2247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T01:33:11.000Z","msg":"一晚 識返飛慶祝下先"},{"pid":"9c01b476e3da5e97fdc748ff7b8ee46331866006","tid":15212,"uid":44071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T01:36:11.000Z","msg":"以前一日一包，一個鐘最小一定要食一飛<br />\n戒咗已經十幾年冇食番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10b021e17eb52b175063871e19069770361ccc2c","tid":15212,"uid":30412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T01:39:22.000Z","msg":"停不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"770465231127631079a4b666fc11de02666faf3f","tid":15212,"uid":24607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T01:41:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上年兩日一包<br />\n而家得閒一兩嗰禮拜先食一兩枝<br />\n食唔食都<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3accaf5d4a7e10f1dd2be043edfc2260b0c329d4","tid":15212,"uid":45858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T01:49:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n本身食咗4-5 年，每日唔食唔得。<br />\n唔想屋企人知，半夜都要落街扯兩咀。返工好喺街好，必都要找地方食先安樂。<br />\n<br />\n突然有日發覺，煙味好嘔心，覺悟到唔想比煙仔控制住日常生活。食吓食吓越食越少，有三年起已經冇買煙了。<br />\n<br />\n巴絲加油，意志可控制一切，唔好比煙仔控制你"},{"pid":"4c9e2b4f0879e0cb8da35bf3b0b30b5ce59cee83","tid":15212,"uid":24366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T01:54:40.000Z","msg":"前日俾東華趕走左<br />\n話我決心唔夠<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21aa1fd8547a0e6fb7b55fcce2c2d33d2ce46b0e","tid":15212,"uid":45858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T02:00:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>前日俾東華趕走左<br />\n話我決心唔夠<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第一步心癮起係好難搞，我都幾次走回頭路食返。<br />\n<br />\n煙仔唔係生活必需品，請記住嘅生活同生命唔好比呢尐嘢支配着"},{"pid":"bf1f53cf8e341efb0ca56b4638c2349ca761680a","tid":15212,"uid":15379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T02:07:18.000Z","msg":"開始緊第四包，好想唔食，但真係好多野煩，當左呢味嘢做寄托<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"248e3d94af708638c94f6f4d159d4e9d58121bf5","tid":15212,"uid":45858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T02:16:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>開始緊第四包，好想唔食，但真係好多野煩，當左呢味嘢做寄托<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n煩(凡)事總會過，但抽多兩咀唔會解決到件事。<br />\n<br />\n煙草中有化學物質可以令你暫時放鬆身體，但長期食落去，身體自然會適應，食到馴咗。你要追求放鬆感覺，自不然越食越多，越食越密。<br />\n<br />\n寄托有好多，例如跑個步，跑半個鐘至一個鐘，吹吹風都可以好relax"},{"pid":"fc1a2a389a40d447199a973b483c616ebd2b0593","tid":15212,"uid":18253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T02:24:02.000Z","msg":"戒左兩年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"405a3efd4e311740ebd45d0c7dc1c03396eb2cc8","tid":15212,"uid":18253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T02:26:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>戒左兩年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係用東華黎幫我戒煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b319e079f96dab232245d895d5fd65115bb640b1","tid":15212,"uid":4644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T02:27:00.000Z","msg":"我連食既原因都唔知係咩<br />\n<br />\n不過大約4日一包，其實我好想介，但係耐唔耐冇野做就會想扯返啖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d98f1567fbde3651396076186ce66854b24791d4","tid":15212,"uid":46882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T15:12:07.000Z","msg":"戒左2星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cf7d76e41723d4052b6e5225fe07a823f5fc10b","tid":15212,"uid":45858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T02:23:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>戒左2星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n繼續努力"},{"pid":"73e8dc0144082aeda776aca599b96c75cd39f094","tid":15212,"uid":16901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T09:15:49.000Z","msg":"食左幾個月，上個禮拜開始決定唔食，但係一有野煩驚又食番，同埋出去飲野就自然想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83eda3f3f938219762801f08bec905444a7edc30","tid":15212,"uid":40264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T09:19:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>戒左2星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你個名"}]}